lead_paragraph: England fast bowler Chris Jordan has joined Indian Premier League (IPL) franchise Royal Challengers Bangalore as a replacement for injured Australia paceman Mitchell Starc, the Indian cricket board said.

headline.print_headline: Jordan Replaces Starc at Bangalore, Mumbai Sign Taylor
